{"tid":2063701,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★葵涌中心買家500元「落訂」購高層單位","createTime":"2020-06-14T08:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T11:31:18.000Z","uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"148307852ea0f7406e48abfccbc4c15b370b98aa","tid":2063701,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:27:13.000Z","msg":"中原許偉業表示，葵涌中心高層G室，實用面積353方呎，單位於4月底以530萬元叫價放售，由於市場多個新盤開削弱購賣力，業主示意510萬元也會考慮，獲區內客即睇即還價至488萬元，議價後終以495萬元成交，呎價14,023元。據稱原業主手上持有16個住宅單位，上址於1987年5月僅以約30萬元購入，至今升值465萬元或約15.5倍。<br />\n<br />\n他續稱，新買家由於未有帶票在身，故仿效早前的成交，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">即場以現金500元「落訂」</span></strong></span>，再即時取支票以支付單位的臨時訂金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200614/bkn-20200614145723013-0614_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200614%2Fbkn-20200614145723013-0614_00842_001.html&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJlGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=a344b345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200614/bkn-20200614145723013-0614_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"993e926c3066b231fb7f33b66ded585e09043bba","tid":2063701,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:27:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01db8f681b8e2da3e3f7b2867292e3ee97732e4","tid":2063701,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:28:15.000Z","msg":"仿效早前的成交，即場以現金500元「落訂」<br />\n仿效早前的成交，即場以現金500元「落訂」"},{"pid":"65bf01e896781f4cc2